response = self.app.get('/%s/actors' % self.api, headers=self.headers,
    query_string={'name': u'.*am.*', '_regex': u'name'})
self.assertEqual(response.status_code, 200)
response_json = json.loads(response.data)
self.assertDictEqual({'total': len(self.actors[0:2]), 'items': self.actors[
    0:2]}, response_json)
